  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Update: Season Festival!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/04ebcb80886f0f440f1c58bb6bd70439.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=281 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New items only for each sensons!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasonal limited animals as well!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e75ef8696ff2451bf55d3d159c5124f3.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=281 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/a1afab2e5a63db37a97e56350a7ca3d5.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Legend has it that in a picturesque beachside wonderland is an age-old Spirit Tree that has been blessing this place since the dawn of time and attracted animals to dwell around it.<br><br>One day, a volcano erupted, laying to waste many parts of the land. The inhabitants take actions, deciding to restore the environment and revive their homeland with the help of Purifying Light.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Merging Brings Happiness and Cures OCD</h2>Create a new home and everything is about merging objects to upgrade. Various items are for you to merge. Collecting and organizing will never end.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/41b13c9308a6a350840c59637b8ef4af.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/41b13c9308a6a350840c59637b8ef4af.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/41b13c9308a6a350840c59637b8ef4af.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Resources with Efficient Recycling Loops</h2>A variety of plants and resource-producing structures require constant merging and planning on the go. Make sure that production and building are in tandem with each other to develop the homeland.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/2de2d47d330b2233fb7dc67bcad7f7c5.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/2de2d47d330b2233fb7dc67bcad7f7c5.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/2de2d47d330b2233fb7dc67bcad7f7c5.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cute Animals Help You</h2>Merging animal balls summons helpers like kittens, bearlings and monkeys to collect stuff for you. Merging animals unlcoks new styles for them to busy themselves in the forest with cuter styles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e39010e65b24b0370dcd87b18a7ce223.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e39010e65b24b0370dcd87b18a7ce223.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e39010e65b24b0370dcd87b18a7ce223.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Develop a Land of Your Own</h2>A great piece of land can be unlocked part by part as you progress in the game. Merge an assortment of items and structures to develop a land of your own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/ebdceb2a7b17462009479f0bcf012002.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/ebdceb2a7b17462009479f0bcf012002.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/ebdceb2a7b17462009479f0bcf012002.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless Unlockables</h2>Tons of animals, plants and structures for you to unlock and fill the Encyclopedia.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/dd41448493060f55e6b8726db40e3184.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Update: Season Festival!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/04ebcb80886f0f440f1c58bb6bd70439.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=281 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New items only for each sensons!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasonal limited animals as well!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e75ef8696ff2451bf55d3d159c5124f3.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=281 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/a1afab2e5a63db37a97e56350a7ca3d5.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Legend has it that in a picturesque beachside wonderland is an age-old Spirit Tree that has been blessing this place since the dawn of time and attracted animals to dwell around it.<br><br>One day, a volcano erupted, laying to waste many parts of the land. The inhabitants take actions, deciding to restore the environment and revive their homeland with the help of Purifying Light.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Merging Brings Happiness and Cures OCD</h2>Create a new home and everything is about merging objects to up